title: UCreate Sketch Diary, 11" x 8-1/2", 70 Sheets
description: This sketch diary contains 70 sheets of standard-weight, sulphite drawing paper that is great for all dry media. Each all-purpose white sheet is acid-free with 94 gsm. Spiral binding on the side works well for portable sketching. Diary is perfect for quick-study sketches and drawings. This diary is great for the beginner and intermediate artist to let their visions come to life.
